# PostHog project token + host for product analytics. When unset, the
# app renders identically without telemetry — src/analytics.ts skips
# posthog.init. Project tokens (phc_*) are safe to expose in the
# client; PostHog treats them as public.
#
# Vite reads either VITE_* or NEXT_PUBLIC_* here — set whichever your
# host prefers. NEXT_PUBLIC_* matches the family site convention.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_PROJECT_TOKEN=
# NEXT_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_HOST=https://us.i.posthog.com
# VITE_POSTHOG_PROJECT_TOKEN=
# VITE_POSTHOG_HOST=https://us.i.posthog.com
